{"id": "art-941", "label": "Art. 941", "title": "Art. 941: Comunicarea hotărârii", "slug": "art-941", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_236816653\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1075\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_236816653\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 941:\nComunicarea hot&#259;rârii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1198402729\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1074\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1198402729\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Dup&#259; ce\nhot&#259;rârea de instituire a m&#259;surii de ocrotire a r&#259;mas\ndefinitiv&#259;, instan&#355;a care a pronun&#355;at-o va comunica, de\nîndat&#259;, dispozitivul acesteia în copie legalizat&#259;, dup&#259; cum\nurmeaz&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1767971507\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1073\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1767971507\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)serviciului public comunitar local de eviden&#355;&#259;\na persoanelor la care na&#351;terea celui pus sub ocrotire este\nînregistrat&#259;, pentru a se face men&#355;iune pe marginea actului de\nna&#351;tere;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_406072921\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1072\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_406072921\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)serviciului sanitar competent, pentru ca acesta s&#259;\ninstituie asupra celui pus sub ocrotire, potrivit legii, o supraveghere\npermanent&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1031434712\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1071\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1031434712\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)biroului de cadastru &#351;i publicitate imobiliar&#259;\ncompetent, pentru notarea în cartea funciar&#259;, când este cazul;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_613829811\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1070\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_613829811\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)registrului comer&#355;ului, dac&#259; persoana pus&#259;\nsub ocrotire este profesionist;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1450770860\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1069\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1450770860\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)Registrului na&#355;ional de eviden&#355;&#259; a\nm&#259;surilor de sprijin &#351;i ocrotire luate de notarul public &#351;i\ninstan&#355;a de tutel&#259;, &#355;inut de Uniunea Na&#355;ional&#259; a\nNotarilor Publici din România.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1345237050\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1068\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1345237050\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (1) sunt aplicabile &#351;i\ninstan&#355;elor învestite cu judecarea c&#259;ilor de atac prev&#259;zute de\nlege.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1759586837\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1067\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Civila%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1759586837\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)În cazul în care cererea de punere sub ocrotire a fost\nrespins&#259;, curatela instituit&#259; pe durata procesului înceteaz&#259; de\ndrept.</span></p>"}